short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Make calls via Yobi right from your browser

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Handle your business communications right from your browser by calling any number via Yobi. 
 
Install the Chrome extension and it automatically adds the option in the context menu to call a selected number in the page. 
 
* Call any phone number in your web browser with ease. 
* Save hours of work time and improve call accuracy. 
 

If you routinely use the Internet for research or sales prospecting, this extension can save you and your staff countless hours per year. 

Changelog for version 0.2.0:
- Fix glitch issue after logging in and leaving the extension in a while.

REQUIREMENTS:  
 
* Windows 8 or newer, MacOS 10.13 or newer.
* Chrome version 88 or newer 
* An active Yobi account
